tion F1.\n\n---\n\n## Key Parameters\n\n| Parameter | Value Used | Effect |\n|-----------|------------|--------|\n| `DURATION` | 25s | More musical context per sample |\n| `TRAIN_SIZE` | 6000 | More augmented training diversity |\n| `EPOCHS_P2` | 7 | Deeper fine-tuning (early stopping guards overfitting) |\n| `LR_P2` | 1e-5 | Safe fine-tune — prevents catastrophic forgetting |\n| `N_TTA` | 7 | More inference crops — lower prediction variance |\n| `NOISE_PROB` | 0.8 | Stronger noise robustness |\n| `GRAD_ACCUM` | 4 | Effective batch size of 24 — more stable gradients |","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## 1. Environment Setup\n\nInstall all required libraries. `transformers` provides the AST model and feature extractor. `librosa` handles audio loading and waveform-level augmentation. `torchmetrics` provides the Macro F1 scorer.","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"!pip install -q transformers librosa torchmetrics","metadata":{},"outputs":[],"execution_count":null},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## 2. Imports\n\nImport all standard libraries used throughout the notebook.","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"import os\nimport random\nimport warnings\nimport numpy as np\nimport pandas as pd\nimport torch\nimport torch.nn as nn\nimport librosa\nimport librosa.display\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\nimport matplotlib.gridspec as gridspec\nfrom collections import defaultdict\nfrom tqdm import tqdm\nfrom torch.utils.data import Dataset, DataLoader\nfrom transformers import (\n    ASTFeatureExtractor,\n    ASTForAudioClassification,\n    get_cosine_schedule_with_warmup\n)\nfrom torchmetrics.classification import MulticlassF1Score\n\nwarnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\nprint(\"All imports successful.\")","metadata":{},"outputs":[],"execution_count":null},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## 3. Reproducibility Seed\n\nSet a global seed across Python, NumPy, and PyTorch so that results are reproducible across runs.","metadata":{}},{"cell_ty